ype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methods</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Properties</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methods</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>Array.isArray()</strong></code> 메서드는 인자가&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a>인지 판별합니다.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>Array.isArray([1, 2, 3]);  // true\nArray.isArray({foo: 123}); // false\nArray.isArray('foobar');   // false\nArray.isArray(undefined);  // false</code>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"구문","title":"구문","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>Array.isArray(<var>obj</var>)</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"매개변수","title":"매개변수","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"obj\"><code>obj</code></dt>\n <dd>검사할 객체.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"반환_값","title":"반환 값","isH3":true,"content":"<p>객체가 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a>라면 <code>true</code>, 아니라면 <code>false</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"설명","title":"설명","isH3":false,"content":"<p>객체가 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a>라면 <code>true</code>를 반환하고, 아니라면 <code>false</code>를 반환합니다.</p>\n\n<p>자세한 정보는&nbsp;<a href=\"https://web.mit.edu/jwalden/www/isArray.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">“Determining with absolute accuracy whether or not a JavaScript object is an array”</a>(자바스크립트 객체가 배열인지 정확히 판별하는 방법)&nbsp;문서를 참조하세요.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>// 모두 true 반환\nArray.isArray([]);\nArray.isArray([1]);\nArray.isArray(new Array());\nArray.isArray(new Array('a', 'b', 'c', 'd'));\nArray.isArray(new Array(3));\n// Array.prototype은 스스로도 배열입니다\nArray.isArray(Array.prototype);\n\n// 모두 false 반환\nArray.isArray();\nArray.isArray({});\nArray.isArray(null);\nArray.isArray(undefined);\nArray.isArray(17);\nArray.isArray('Array');\nArray.isArray(true);\nArray.isArray(false);\nArray.isArray({ __proto__: Array.prototype });</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instanceof_vs_isarray","title":"<code>instanceof</code> vs <code>isArray</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>Array</code>&nbsp;객체를 판별할 때, <code>Array.isArray</code>는 <code>iframe</code>을&nbsp;통해서도 작동하기 때문에 <code>instanceof</code>&nbsp;보다&nbsp;적합합니다.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>var iframe = document.createElement('iframe');\ndocument.body.appendChild(iframe);\nxArray = window.frames[window.frames.length-1].Array;\nvar arr = new xArray(1,2,3); // [1,2,3]\n\n// 올바른 Array 판별\nArray.isArray(arr);  // true\n// iframe을 통해서 작동하지 않기 때문에 올바르지 않은 방법\narr instanceof Array; // false</code>\n</pre>","titleAsText":"instanceof vs isArray"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"폴리필","title":"폴리필","isH3":false,"content":"<p>아래 코드를 실행하면&nbsp;지원하지 않는 환경에서도 <code>Array.isArray()</code>를 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>Array<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isArray<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  Array<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">isArray</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">arg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'[object Array]'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"명세","title":"명세","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">명세</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">상태</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">주석</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.4.3.2\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'Array.isArray' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>초안. 자바스크립트 1.8.5 에 구현됨.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-array.isarray\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'Array.isArray' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-array.isarray\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'Array.isArray' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Array.isArray","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/isArray/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"참고","title":"참고","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"구문","id":"구문"},{"text":"설명","id":"설명"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"폴리필","id":"폴리필"},{"text":"명세","id":"명세"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"},{"text":"참고","id":"참고"}],"summary":"Array.isArray() 메서드는 인자가 Array인지 판별합니다.","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Array.isArray()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/isarray","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/array/isarray/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript 참고서"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"표준 내장 객체"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array","title":"Array"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/isArray","title":"Array.isArray()"}],"pageTitle":"Array.isArray() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}